 secondes.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le premier\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"de Khelif\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"aux Jeux de Paris\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"mais la boxeuse italienne a abandonn\\u00e9 le match apr\\u00e8s\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"46 secondes\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apr\\u00e8s avoir re\\u00e7u un coup de poing au visage, Carini s'est retir\\u00e9e dans le coin et a abandonn\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9998420679819361, \"rank\": 0.00015795696455871892, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 0.9999999996232418, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coin\", \"score\": 0.9999997328382407, \"rank\": 2.458847586989018e-07, \"text\": \"coin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Apr\\u00e8s avoir re\\u00e7u un cou